quran[9]{c,v,t,f}:
  15,67,"Niŵaiche (kwa Lutwi) ŵandu ŵa mu nsinda ali ŵakusengwa (pakupikana kuti ayiche achachanda ŵakusalala kuti ŵatende yausakwa)."
  15,68,"(Lutwi) jwatite: “Chisimu ŵanganyaŵa achalendo ŵangu, basi nkandesya soni (pakwatenda yakusakala).”"
  15,69,"“Ni mun’jogope Allah soni nkanjigasya nchesela (pameso pao).”"
  16,46,"Kapena kwakwembekanya ŵanganyao mu kwendajenda kwao, kutendaga ŵanganyao nganaŵa ŵanti nikunnepelekasya (Allah kwapa ipotesi)?"
  16,47,"Kapena kwakwembekanya aku ali ni woga (wakwembecheya kwapata ilagasyo pakwapungula jumojumo mpaka kumala wosope)? Basi chisimu M’mbuje gwenu ni Mpole kusyene, Jwachanasa channope."
  16,48,"Ana nganaiona ichindu yaagumbile Allah yaikupendama iwulili yakwe chakun’dyo ni kunchiji kunsujudila Allah aku ili yakulinandiya?"
  17,13,"Soni mundu jwalijose tuntaŵilile itendo yakwe nnukosi mwakwe, ni chitukankopochesye lisiku lya Kiyama chitabu chachakachisimane chili cheunukuleunukule."
  17,14,"(Chakasalilidwe kuti): “Soomaani chitabu chenu, mmwejo mwasyene lelo nkukwanila kuliŵalanjila (itendo yenu).”"
  17,15,"Mundu jwaajongweche, basi nikuti akongoka kwakulikamuchisya nsyene, soni jwasochelele, basi nikuti akusochelela kwaalikonya nsyene, soni jwaatwiichiile nsigo (wasambi) ngasaja kutwichila nsigo wajwine, soni Uwwe nganituŵa ŵakupeleka ilagasyo mpaka tukatumisye (kaje) ntenga."